      • load

        public static int load(java.lang.String path,
                       java.lang.Boolean initscan)
        Method load read JSON file and drill datas from it It drills index(description), type(name), postdate and properities
        Parameters:
        path - refers to path to JSON file.
        initscan - signals, if method must initializate scanner which will read JSON file.
        Returns:
        2 if file is not found, 1 if there is anything left in file, 0 is drilling is complete

      • createIndex

        public static int createIndex()
        Method createIndex creates index according to datas from JSON file. It also adds postDate, which refers to time when index was created in elastic search.
        Returns:
        0 if succesfull, 1 if error
